Documents relating to the classification of R 18+ films 'Overlord', 'Sensitive New Age Killer', 'Taxi Driver', 'Taxi Driver—Making Taxi Driver', 'Sleepers'.
These documents describe material that has been classified as suitable for individuals over the age of 18 years. R 18+ material is restricted to adults as it contains content that is considered high in impact for viewers.
This includes content that may be offensive to sections of the community.
If you wish to obtain a copy of these documents, please contact us at foi@infrastructure.gov.au so we may consider your request further.
